    intro: "'How many weeks pregnant am I?' is one of the most common questions every expectant mother asks. This pregnancy week calculator instantly tells you your exact gestational age in weeks and days based on your last menstrual period (LMP). Pregnancy is divided into three trimesters — First (weeks 1-12), Second (weeks 13-27), and Third (weeks 28-40) — each with unique developmental milestones for your baby and important medical checkpoints for you. In India, tracking pregnancy weeks is essential for scheduling the right prenatal tests at the right time: NT scan at 11-14 weeks, anomaly scan at 18-22 weeks, and growth scans at 32-36 weeks. Whether you're tracking your pregnancy on the Practo or BabyChakra app, or simply keeping notes — knowing your exact week helps you stay on top of your prenatal care schedule.",
