    intro: "Whether you're hitting the gym for the first time or you're a seasoned fitness enthusiast, knowing your exact calorie needs is what separates results from frustration. This fitness calorie calculator is designed for Indian gym-goers and athletes, providing precise calorie targets for three common goals: Cutting (fat loss while preserving muscle), Maintenance (sustaining current physique), and Bulking (building muscle mass). The Indian fitness industry is booming — from Gold's Gym and Cult.fit memberships to home workout culture. But without accurate nutrition, your gym efforts are wasted. This tool uses the Mifflin-St Jeor equation with activity-adjusted multipliers to give you a science-backed calorie target that works whether you follow a vegetarian gym diet (paneer, soy, whey) or non-vegetarian (chicken, eggs, fish).",
