    intro: "Fat loss — not just 'weight loss' — is what truly improves health and body composition. When you lose weight through crash diets or extreme calorie restriction, you lose both fat AND muscle. But when you lose fat specifically through a moderate calorie deficit combined with strength training and adequate protein, you maintain or even build muscle while shedding fat. This distinction is crucial for Indians who already tend to have lower muscle mass and higher body fat (the 'thin-fat' phenotype). This fat loss calculator computes your exact calorie target for optimal fat loss while preserving lean muscle mass. Designed for Indian body types, dietary patterns, and lifestyle, it provides sustainable targets that work whether you eat roti-sabzi, rice-sambar, or modern fusion meals.",
